cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.RO 

This paper deals with computer vision and natural language processing, which are the main topics of cs.CV and cs.CL. The use of RNNs and message passing also suggests that the paper could belong to cs.AI and cs.LG. Additionally, the use of scene graphs and their application in robotics and autonomous systems could also make this paper relevant to cs.RO.
